# Visit counter storage — see README.md "Analytics setup" for step-by-step
# instructions. The site works fine with these unset; the counter and
# /stats page just stay hidden until they're configured.
#
# Either an Upstash Redis database (used directly) or a Vercel KV store
# (Vercel-managed, Upstash-backed) works — copy whichever REST URL/token
# you're given into these two names.
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=
